Package com.kallasoft.smugmug.api.json

Interface Summary
Method Interface used to define a method in the kallasoft SmugMug Java API.
 

Class Summary
AbstractMethod Class used to represent the base implementation of a Method in the kallasoft SmugMug Java API.
AbstractResponse A class that provides the base implementation of a response from the SmugMug JSON API methods.
 

Exception Summary
RuntimeJSONException A class used to convert a JSONException (checked exception) to a RuntimeException so it can either be ignored or handled by the caller easily.
